r(n)=\sum_{k=0}^{m-1}10^{m-1-k}\left(\left\lfloor\frac{n}{10^k}\right\rfloor-10\left\lfloor\frac1{10}\left\lfloor\frac{n}{10^k}\right\rfloor\right\rfloor\right)
